# 14. Common Troubleshooting

## Authentication Failed

Test:

```bash
sudo doveadm auth test USERNAME
```

Reset password:

```bash
sudo passwd USERNAME
```

---

## Postfix Not Sending

Check:

```bash
sudo postfix check
```

Logs:

```bash
sudo tail -100 /var/log/mail.log
```

---

## Dovecot Won't Start

Validate:

```bash
sudo doveconf
```

---

## Certificate Issues

Renew:

```bash
sudo certbot renew --dry-run
```

---

## Firewall

Allow:

```bash
sudo ufw allow 25

sudo ufw allow 587

sudo ufw allow 143

sudo ufw allow 993
```

